}

\subtree{
\title{Error Messages}
\pre{\startverb
| Error | Meaning | Fix |
|-------|---------|-----|
| `PR missing GF(3) section` | No skill manifest | Add `## GF(3) Skill Coloring` section |
| `GF(3) not conserved` | Σ ≠ 0 (mod 3) | Add balancing skills |
| `Invalid trit value` | Not in {-1, 0, +1} | Use ⊖/○/⊕ symbols |
| `Missing thread ID` | No `⟨xxxx⟩` | Link to ampcode thread |
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Operator Algebra}
\p{Skills combine via tensor product (⊗):}

\pre{\startverb
⟦s₁ ⊗ s₂⟧ = (trit₁ + trit₂, mix(color₁, color₂), xor(seed₁, seed₂))
\stopverb}

\p{Conservation law:}

\pre{\startverb
∀ PR: Σᵢ tritᵢ ≡ 0 (mod 3)
\stopverb}

\p{This ensures the skill lattice remains balanced across all contributions.}
}

\subtree{
\title{Cat# Integration}
\p{This skill maps to \strong{Cat# = Comod(P)} as a bicomodule in the equipment structure:}

\pre{\startverb
Trit: 0 (ERGODIC)
Home: Prof
