Color: #26D826
\stopverb}

\subtree{
\title{GF(3) Naturality}
\p{The skill participates in triads satisfying:}

\pre{\startverb
(-1) + (0) + (+1) ≡ 0 (mod 3)
\stopverb}

\p{This ensures compositional coherence in the Cat# equipment structure.}
}
}
}